divs: sighting detailswhile walking to the bus stop at around 6:25am 09\20\12 i looked up at the western sky and saw an pulsating orange light behind a cloud. it lasted at least 10 minutes, it was still there when the bus arrived.
Summary: Orange flashing light in western sky behind cloud in early morning.
